Multiflash Privacy Policy


No personal information is collected by this app, no information is shared. The app gathers no data from the phone. 

The only permission required by this app is for access to the camera in order to use its flash's torch functionality.

Multiflash is a packaged app, so the program data remains on the phone and requires no network connection.

This app may receive updates from the Firefox Marketplace to improve its interface and/or functionality.

The source code for Multiflash is freely available at www.github.com/mdq3/multiflash 

Multiflash is relased under the GNU General Public License version 3.

If you have any suggestions, bug reports or wish to contribute to the development of this app, please contact me through my GitHub page at www.github.com/mdq3 or submit an issue to the app's repository.

